### Overview

Basic usage of mbSlider and uses all default settings. The structure works with any kind of DOM element. In this example we use `<div class="item">...</div>` but you could put any other element `div/span/a/img...`

### Setup
```
$(document).ready(function(){
  $('#demoSlider').mbSlider({
     mode: 'fade'
  });
});
```
